snippet.title: Kamaeru: A Frog Refuge - Official Launch Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2024
snippet.description: Kamaeru: A Frog Refuge is a casual simulation game developed by Humble Reeds. Foster a sanctuary for fros and restore the biodiversity of the wetlands in Kamaeru, a cozy farming sim where you raise frogs by playing mini-games and decorating your habitat. Hop right to it! Kamaeru: A Frog Refuge is available now for Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and PC (Steam).
